snippet: Chile's emergency office ordered a preventive evacuation of the coastline in the country's north following an earthquake of magnitude 7.8 late on Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Chile Orders Preventive Evacuation of Northern Coastline
headline.main: Chile Orders Preventive Evacuation of Northern Coastline

lead_paragraph: Chile's emergency office ordered a preventive evacuation of the coastline in the country's north following an earthquake of magnitude 7.8 late on Wednesday.
